RACE.FOOTNOTES: WINGS LIKE EAGLES showed the way in hand just off the inside, tucked inside through the turn coming under coaxing at the five-sixteenths, spun three wide for home and drew off under a drive kept to task. CHARGING LADY coaxed from the start, chased three then two wide coming under coaxing half a mile from home, went three to four wide through the turn, angled six to seven wide into upper stretch and kicked on belatedly to procure the show honors. SHE'S MO BUBBLY broke in at the start bumping DOLCE SERA, chased four then three wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, swung four wide into upper stretch and weakened in the late going. SOURCING NETWORK coaxed from the start, chased three then two wide under coaxing from three furlongs out, angled five wide into upper stretch and weakened. ALL TIMES WERE HAND-TIMED AND PROVIDED BY NYRA DUE TO A TIMING ISSUE

GRACEFULNESS raced just off the pace on the outside, dropped back under urging late on the backstretch, went four wide around the turn and came up empty.
